values:
Yeeess!!!  I'm back on the road again )))) 
After 16 days of crazy bikin', old monk drinkin', acid dancin' and beach missin' @ Goa....  VNEZAPNO11:



27-02 dep Madgaon at 7-45, arr Hospet at 14-53 by Howra Express Sleeper class - 352km @ Rs 180 only
- day chillin' at Hampi rocks, still drinkin' exported Old Monk, ridin' Bajaj and watching sunset at Monkey Temple mountain

 01-03 dep Hospet at 14-55, arr Khurda Road JN on 02-03 at 14-40 by Howra Exp 3AC - 1309km @ Rs 1072 only
- non confirned reservation, but travel I must - sitting on a backpack @ sleeper class 12 hours, then transfered to my place by vzyatka @ 200 rupies only for another 12 hour sleep

02-03 dep Khudra Road JN at 17-10, arr Puri at sunset by Surat-Puri Express II class - 44km @ Rs 30 only
- taking part at Shivaratri fest, making friends at fisherman village and all day bajaj-biking to amazing Chilika lake 

04-03 dep Puri at 22-50, arr Howrah (Calcutta) on 05-03 at 8-10 by Srijagannath Exp Sleeper class - 502km @ Rs 299 only
- so here I am writing this message at Calcutta web-cafe (the city is actually very nice))) waiting 4 the next train... 

05-03 dep Howrah at 17-35, arr New Jalpaiguri on 06-03 at 6-15 by Kampur Exp Sleeper class - 564km @ Rs 249 only

06-03 (really hope so!!!) dep New Jailpaiguri at 09-00 on the Toy Train to Darjeeling  !!!    

Full cash + distance statisticss for this short and intence Indian trip will be updated here soon + pics and detailed trip report coming, so... see you all on the road and some of you in Nepal (!!!) and...
PLEASE BE HAPPY WHEREVER YOU ARE!!!  ;)
